sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Company (Buyer)
  participant F as Find Vendor Mode
  participant V as Vendors
  participant R as RFP Document
  participant S as Score Contracts Mode

  C->>F: Describe project requirements
  F-->>C: Shortlisted vendors

  C->>R: Draft RFP based on requirements
  C->>V: Send RFP to shortlisted vendors

  V-->>C: Send proposals & draft contracts

  C->>S: Upload vendor contracts & criteria
  S-->>C: Scores, comparisons & best contract recommendation

